<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title, description }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-page text-text-primary font-body antialiased overflow-x-hidden">
  <canvas id="dot-grid" class="fixed inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div id="cursor-glow" class="fixed w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-50%, -50%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="relative z-10 pt-20">
    <section class="py-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] items-center">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Vision Map</span>
            <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">Turn “we should use AI” into a real implementation roadmap.</h1>
            <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
              The Vision Map is for teams that know AI matters but need clarity on priorities, sequencing, systems, and the order that will actually create leverage.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              <a href="https://calendly.com/cosminlungu/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Book a Call</a>
              <a href="/ai-audit" class="rounded-xl border border-border-subtle px-8 py-4 text-text-secondary font-semibold transition-colors hover:border-text-muted hover:text-text-primary">Start With the Audit</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-10">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Typical outputs</p>
            <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/40 p-5">
                <p class="font-display font-bold">Priority sequence</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">Which use cases should happen first, and which ones are distractions right now.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/40 p-5">
                <p class="font-display font-bold">System architecture</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">What needs to connect, where data moves, and which tools should own each part of the workflow.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-subtle bg-page/40 p-5">
                <p class="font-display font-bold">Implementation phases</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">A staged roadmap that makes the work manageable and easier to justify internally.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-14 text-center">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">What It Solves</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Useful when the ambition is clear but the path is not</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="glass-card p-8" data-tilt>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold">Too many ideas</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Your team has a long list of AI opportunities, but no way to separate what matters from what is just interesting.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-8" data-tilt>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold">No sequence</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">You need to know what should be designed first, what depends on other systems, and where a smaller proof point should happen before a larger rollout.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-8" data-tilt>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold">Unclear ownership</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">You need a map of which tools, workflows, and teams are involved before implementation can begin cleanly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">How It Works</span>
          <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <div>
              <p class="text-4xl font-display font-black text-accent">01</p>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-display font-bold">Discovery</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">We review the business model, operational constraints, current stack, and the list of desired AI outcomes.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-4xl font-display font-black text-accent">02</p>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-display font-bold">Mapping</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">I translate that into a structured system view: priorities, dependencies, risk areas, and where ROI is most likely to show up first.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-4xl font-display font-black text-accent">03</p>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-display font-bold">Roadmap</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">You get a clear plan the team can align around, whether implementation happens with me, internally, or with another partner.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm lg:pb-section">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Next Step</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Need clarity before committing to implementation?</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            The Vision Map is the bridge between broad AI ambition and a build sequence your business can actually execute.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10">
            <a href="https://calendly.com/cosminlungu/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Discuss the Vision Map</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/dot-grid.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/magnetic.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/tilt.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
